OL,3,CBelfast traffic chaos as part of
OL,4,Cmotorway closed
OL,6,FThe infrastructure minister has
OL,7,Fdefended road works which caused
OL,8,Ftraffic chaos over the weekend in
OL,9,FBelfast, saying there was no other
OL,10,Foption.
OL,12,FSuch was the congestion, motorists
OL,13,Fwere faced with delays over an hour
OL,14,Ffor journeys which normally take
OL,15,Fminutes.
OL,17,FThere were queues of more than an hour
OL,18,Fand tailbacks stretching miles with
OL,19,Fpart of a major motorway closed. And
OL,20,Fmore work is planned.
