OL,4,Cmotorway closed
OL,6,FMinister Liz Kimmins acknowledged the
OL,7,Finconvenience and frustration the
OL,8,Fworks caused. The Sinn Fein MLA
OL,9,Fstressed the work was essential as
OL,10,Fpart of a major safety upgrade.
OL,12,FThe eastbound carriageway of the M3
OL,13,Fbetween Nelson Street and D Street was
OL,14,Fclosed on Friday until 6am on Monday
OL,15,Fmorning, which meant no access to the
OL,16,FM3 bridge towards Bangor until just
OL,17,Fafter the Titanic quarter.
