OL,3,CBelfast traffic chaos as part of
OL,4,Cmotorway closed
OL,6,FIt forced drivers from the north into
OL,7,Ffewer lanes on the M2 or to take a
OL,8,Fdiversion onto roads like the A2 shore
OL,9,FRoad.
OL,11,FDUP MLA Phillip Brett said: "The
OL,12,Fdepartment wanted to close the busiest
OL,13,Froad in Belfast where 80,000 cars
OL,14,Ftravel on a daily basis over a
OL,15,Fweekend, a weekend that was the first
OL,16,Fpayday weekend of the summer break.
