OL,3,CBelfast traffic chaos as part of
OL,4,Cmotorway closed
OL,6,F"We had road closures in place, but
OL,7,Ftraffic lights not sync to those and
OL,8,Fwe had road users on Friday and
OL,9,FSaturday, stuck in our city centre,
OL,10,Falternative routes into our city
OL,11,Fcompletely blocked at a time when
OL,12,Fbusinesses are really struggling.
OL,14,F"This was a payday weekend and people
OL,15,Fwere keen to get in and support the
OL,16,Flocal economy, and people were unable
OL,17,Fto get into our capital city."
