OL,3,CBelfast traffic chaos as part of
OL,4,Cmotorway closed
OL,6,FThe works are part of a #400,000
OL,7,Fmaintenance scheme from the Department
OL,8,Ffor Infrastructure, but this isn't the
OL,9,Fnew scenario - at Christmas, commuters
OL,10,Falso face disruption due to road works.
OL,12,FInfrastructure Minister Liz Kimmins
OL,13,Fsaid: "Initially, when the works were
OL,14,Fdone last year, we had indicated at
OL,15,Fthat point that further works would
OL,16,Fpotentially be required this summer
OL,17,Fand again potentially in summer 2026.
OL,19,F"So at the most earliest stage we have
OL,20,Ftried to ensure there has been
OL,21,Fadvanced warning on that.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
