OL,3,CBelfast traffic chaos as part of
OL,4,Cmotorway closed
OL,6,F"It's not to underestimate how
OL,7,Ffrustrating that is for many road
OL,8,Fusers and potentially the wider area,
OL,9,Fhowever, I think it's really important
OL,10,Fto stress that this is absolutely
OL,11,Fessential.
OL,13,F"It's major safety work that's
OL,14,Frequired, and we cannot let it go on
OL,15,Funtil maybe a point where that weakens
OL,16,Ffurther, and it's important that we
OL,17,Fget that work done."
